, (residual sum of squared error (RSS)) .

, . RSS_root.

, : RSS_root (RSS(L) + RSS(R))

, Y, RSS_root - (0 + 0) = RSS_root

age.pred = predict(tree.bank, bank.test)

# TSS - Total Sum of Squares
tss = sum((mean(bank.test$age) - bank.test$age)^2) 
# R^2 -
